2004/12/21:
  * WinInstaller: Store path in registry for easier updating to future versions
    [#1088111]
  * Add Clients/Sources2 columns to the download table.  These are numbers reported
    by mldonkey rather than calculated based on what mldonkey sends. (mldonkey is
    not consistent, so everything is optional for you to choose, and these numbers
    are only updated when the full file is refreshed).  The mldonkey gui protocol is
    far from intelligent.  Use the TableColumn selector to re-order/choose columns 
    you want. (see faq)
