2004/08/20:
  * Fix ArrayOOB in console [#1007071][#1013491]
  * Preferences->Transfers->Preview
  In addition to specifying an app to use to preview files locally,
  you can also select different apps to spawn based on file extension. The
  main preview app must be filled it -- it becomes the default [#1012362]
  - input an extension and a program and "Add" it to the list
  - select an entry from the list and press "Remove" to remove it
  ie:  mp3 = c:\mp3player\mp3player.exe
       avi = /usr/local/bin/aviplayer
       txt = d:\windows\system32\notepad.exe

