2004/06/24:
  * Update donkeyfakes URL [#970393]

2004/06/07:
  * Added optional tab categories to the download table [#913455]
  	Usage:   
    - first, click the upper left icon on the downloads table and
      "toggle tabs on" from the menu
    - Add/remove tabs by right clicking on an existing tab and using the popup
  	  context menu
    - Apply filters (in the upper left icon menu (Show->) or type something in
      the refine search regular expression filter) and they will apply 
      exclusively to the active tab
      ex: "Tab 1" Show->Donkey+FastTrack + Audio files with Regex "nas|jay"
          "Videos from Bittorrent" Show->Bittorrent + Video files 
          "My jpg files" Show->Image files with Regex "jpg"
          "All downloads" Show->All
          etc...
    - tabs are on the bottom by default - toggle in preferences->transfers
    - drag and drop tabs to reorder them 
    - with a ton of files, filtering/redrawing is faster with chunk graphs off

